name: Judgment Parade
description:
" Judgment Parade "

The media are still discussing issues of dissent. Even recently emerged news that is still hot. Various parties accuse each other, attack each other, judge each other, feel each other is the most right. I'm sick and tired of this mess! this work is an interpretation of fanfare in a judgment show. Various positive and negative thoughts revel in the head. Monitor the noisy and trapped surroundings. I'm really bored, I'm really bored! Now peace is no longer a dream.

1312 x 1500 Pixels
30 fps
